// English Control Flow - If/Otherwise conditionals
This module is test.controlflow.

Define Decision with approved, reason.

// Simple if condition
To isAdult with age, produce:
  If age greater than 17:
    Return true.
  Return false.

// If with otherwise
To checkAge with age, produce:
  If age less than 18:
    Return "Minor".
  Otherwise:
    Return "Adult".

// Nested conditions
To categorizeAge with age, produce:
  If age less than 13:
    Return "Child".
  If age less than 20:
    Return "Teenager".
  If age less than 60:
    Return "Adult".
  Return "Senior".

// Complex decision logic
To evaluateApplication with age, score, produce:
  If age less than 18:
    Return Decision with approved = false, reason = "Underage applicant".
  If score less than 600:
    Return Decision with approved = false, reason = "Score too low".
  Return Decision with approved = true, reason = "Approved".
